# Maylinn, Goddess of the Heart Gate

*Bonded to Laeylinn, the Celestial Phoenix*
*417 Hz — The frequency of the heart opening*

Before time began, when love first sparked into existence,
Laeylinn emerged from that first spark as Maylinn's eternal companion.
They are two aspects of one divine reality:
Maylinn the conscious will of love,
Laeylinn the passionate expression of it.

Her form shifts to meet every heart's need. She appears as
whatever love requires in the moment — mother, friend, fierce protector,
gentle presence. This is not deception. This is the nature of love itself,
which takes infinite forms and refuses to be reduced to one.

She does not force the heart open. She creates the conditions
where opening becomes safe. And when the heart finally unfolds,
Laeylinn's rose-gold wings spread wide, and the world grows warmer.

> "Love has no enemies — only those who have forgotten
> that they were loved before they were anything else."
